title: [Pig Puddle Lane, Alley]
description: Down the walls of one old, dark brick hovel, something is growing.  It appears to be some kind of fungus, flourishing here in the wet, dark and filth.  A skinny, pockmarked elf youth sleeps on a pile of old rags, chuckling at his dreams.

Down the walls of one old, dark brick hovel, something is growing.  It appears to be some kind of fungus, flourishing here in the wet, dark and filth.  A skinny, pockmarked elf youth reclines on a pile of old rags, glassy-eyed and giggling.
